Pancreatic Cancer</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"18px\",\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"400\"}},\"fontFamily\":\"roboto-flex\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-roboto-flex-font-family\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">The Andy Schram Foundation for Pancreatic Cancer Relief is dedicated to alleviating the burdens faced by families and individuals affected by pancreatic cancer. Our mission is to provide comprehensive support through financial assistance and non-financial resources, ensuring that those impacted can focus on what truly matters-healing and cherishing moments with loved ones.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"10%\",\"bottom\":\"10%\",\"left\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"padding-top:10%;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:10%;padding-left:0\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#262626\"}}},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#262626\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"40px\",\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"800\"}},\"fontFamily\":\"figtree\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color has-link-color has-figtree-font-family\" style=\"color:#262626;font-size:40px;font-style:normal;font-weight:800\">Our Funds<br>Are Utilized to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"800\",\"fontSize\":\"40px\"}},\"fontFamily\":\"figtree\",\"conditionalBlocks\":{\"sets\":[{\"id\":\"9b313712-eaf7-401a-a7f9-ff5568e69ee9\",\"type\":\"set\",\"conditions\":[{\"id\":\"8ed797ea-76d5-4a40-9d6e-82fe22d989dc\",\"type\":\"responsiveScreenSizes\",\"showOn\":[\"showTabletScreen\",\"showDesktopScreen\"]}]}]}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-figtree-font-family\" style=\"font-si